-- Lehman's Chapter 11 plan gets creditor support
-- 
-- Wed Oct 26, 2011 1:49am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/26/us-lehman-idUSTRE79P10920111026

 

 (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEHMQ.PK said its Chapter 11 reorganization plan is now supported by creditors who hold more than $160 billion in claims. 
 The U.S. brokerage said it filed a supplement to the joint Chapter 11 plan which includes nine major settlement agreements. Lehman said the deadline for voting for the plan is November 4. (Reporting by Maneesha Tiwari in Bangalore)